        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer146570362" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10508124169417482233">I enjoyed this novel. A complicated anti-hero. a vampire with a will of iron and a strong sense of ethics, admirable female characters, complicated plot involving evil sorcerer priests persecuting vampires and controling demons out to commit genocide against the vampire race. Bad vampires fighting for their lives and trying to evolve in the end. self-sacrifice of hero at the end.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


