<span id="freeTextContainer14770411920728511092"><strong>Excited to begin this series of books!</strong><br/><br/>Great beginning. Characters are vividly described and set up for very active parts in this well focused story line. Peter Octavian is one of my new heroes for his selflessness, cool 60&apos;s attitude and style, and ability to control his shape shifting to what is needed at the time.I am Ready to read book #2. While this book does not need a follow up book, there are just enough proficies and questions left to keep the intrigue burning for book #2.<br/><br/><br/><br/> to</span>
